The '''Racing Club de Koumassi''' (RC Koumassi) is an [[Côte d'Ivoire|ivorian]] [[football (soccer)|football]] club based in [[Koumassi]]. Currently, the club plays in Ivory Coast's second Division Poule Abidjan.

