The '''Ruhuna Rugby Football Union''' (RRFU) is the governing body for [[rugby union]] in [[Southern Province, Sri Lanka|Southern Province]], [[Sri Lanka]]. Its president was [[Kumar Abeywardena]] until he resigned on June 12, 2010.<ref>http://www.dailymirror.lk/print/index.php/sports/128-local/13373.html</ref>

