{{infobox volleyball club | clubname = Tricolorul LMV Ploiești | image = [[File:Tricolorul_LMV_Ploiești_logo.png|150px]] | short name = LMV; Tricolorul | fullname = | founded = {{Start date and years ago|df=yes|2007}} | ground = [[Olimpia Sports Hall|Sala Olimpia]] | capacity = 3,000 | chairman = | manager = | league = [[Divizia A1 (men's volleyball)|Divizia A1]] | season = [[2017–18 Divizia A1 (men's volleyball)|2017–18]] | position = Divizia A1, 1st | website = https://tricolorullmvploiesti.ro/ }}
'''Tricolorul LMV Ploiești''' is a professional men's [[volleyball]] club based in [[Ploiești]], [[Romania]], that competes in the [[2018–19 CEV Challenge Cup|CEV Challenge Cup]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cev.eu/Competition-Area/CompetitionTeamDetails.aspx?TeamID=11231&ID=1116|title=Tricolorul MVP PLOIESTI |work=[[European Volleyball Confederation|CEV]]|accessdate=26 September 2018}}</ref>
== Honours == === Domestic === * '''[[Divizia A1 (men's volleyball)|Divizia A1]]''' : '''Winners (1):''' [[2017–18 Divizia A1 (men's volleyball)|2018]] * '''Cupa României''' : '''Winners (1):''' 2018
